                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="13773191" author="beobal" created="Fri, 20 Sep 2013 17:08:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This is caused by an additional ColumnDef being added in the CfDef used to construct the Pig schema. Where a value_alias is specified for the compact value column, CqlStorage.getKeysMeta adds a ColumnDef for it. The additional one is then added in AbstractCassandaStorage.getColumnMeta, so I&apos;ve added an additional boolean arg to indicate whether the the value_alias has already been processed. I&apos;ve also refactored ACS.getColumnMeta a bit to (hopefully) make the logic clearer. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13774822" author="alexliu68" created="Mon, 23 Sep 2013 18:26:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1 except that I notice the patch is not based on current cassandra-1.2 branch, so it needs be updated to cassandra-1.2 branch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13776467" author="beobal" created="Tue, 24 Sep 2013 16:45:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sorry about that, updated patch attached&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13776476" author="alexliu68" created="Tue, 24 Sep 2013 16:56:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13778934" author="brandon.williams" created="Thu, 26 Sep 2013 16:05:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Can you rebase &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=beobal&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;beobal&quot;&gt;beobal&lt;/a&gt;? We committed a few pig things yesterday and it no longer applies &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/sad.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13779080" author="beobal" created="Thu, 26 Sep 2013 18:40:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;attached rebased patch&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13779092" author="brandon.williams" created="Thu, 26 Sep 2013 18:54:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed, thanks&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
